    <item>
      <title>Timed On/Off Switching Signal Tag</title>
      <author>FrozenMuncher</author>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/661398</link>
      <comments>https://gamebanana.com/mods/661398#PostsListModule</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">dc11406cbe49f64942f542eff28ee40a6c46d170</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 17:18:13 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69badd9e3a613.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/69baddd04c98a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;A signal tag that switches a signal on and off periodically. It has multiple settings to expand its use-cases.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;These are the settings and what they do:&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;b&gt;MapFrameOn&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/code&gt;: Number of frames the signal stays on&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;b&gt;MapFrameOff&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/code&gt;: Number of frames the signal stays off&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;b&gt;RepeatNum&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/code&gt;: Number of times the signal gets turned on or off (note that both turning on and turning off are counted here, meaning a value of 1 means it only turns on, while a value of 2 means it turns on once and then off once). A value of 0 means it switches indefinitely.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="SelectedElement"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;b&gt;IsStartSignalOn&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/code&gt;: The actor starts with the signal being on&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;Usage&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;To add this actor into your mod, copy the &lt;code&gt;.pack.zs&lt;/code&gt; file into your mod's &lt;code&gt;romfs/Pack/Actor/&lt;/code&gt; folder and add the yaml entries you find in &lt;code&gt;ActorInfo.txt&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;GameActorInfo.txt&lt;/code&gt; to their respective files inside &lt;code&gt;romfs/RSDB/&lt;/code&gt;.</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/timedonoffsignaltag.zip" type="application/zip"/>
      <category>Custom Actors</category>
      <category>Custom Actors</category>
    </item>
